			<div class="content" id="post-content-2746128">
									

<p>This is a tale that I've been mulling over for quite a while now, and I recently decided to spruce it up and post it. Not the most surprising ending (or maybe all of you are just cynical bastards), but I hope you enjoy nonetheless.</p>
